<h1>📝 물품 상세 보기</h1>

<p><strong>제목:</strong> {{item.title}}</p>
<p><strong>가격:</strong> {{item.price}}원</p>
<p><strong>상태:</strong> {{item.status}}</p>
<p><strong>설명:</strong> {{item.description}}</p>
